Invocation Name: random radio
des:
Random radio online.

To start, just say "Alexa, random radio".

If you don't like the radio, you can change it saying "Alexa, next".

You can stop anytime, by saying "Alexa, stop".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
